title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Lunar New Year Gifts
content:
Log in to play GTA Online through February 12 to receive a collection of Lunar New Year gifts, including the Black Snake Yogarishima Outfit, Red Serpent Leather Jacket, Snake Soul Pendant, Snake King Pendant, Red Snake Soul Cap, and Gray Snake King Cap.

Plus, finding all 36 Yuanbao Collectibles before February 12 will get you the Gold Snake Santo Capra Outfit.
